Billionaire  Gennady Timchenko , a co-
owner of oil trader Gunvor Group Ltd. and Russian natural-gas
producer OAO Novatek, was elected chairman of the country’s
Kontinental Hockey League, according to its  website .  To contact the reporter on this story:
